Package: TestTrek
Type: Package
Title: Automated Statistical Test Recommender
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Giovanni Briganti
Maintainer: Giovanni Briganti <giovanni.briganti@hotmail.comL>
Description: TestTrek provides an automated recommendation system for choosing 
    the appropriate statistical tests based on the nature of the data. It covers 
    both independent and dependent sample scenarios, and integrates a wide range 
    of common statistical tests, ensuring that users can navigate the complex 
    landscape of statistical testing with ease.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    car
Suggests:
    roxygen2,
    devtools,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
